==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inadvertent
<hw>In`ad*vert"ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>inadvertant</ets>. See 2d <er>In-</er>, and <er>Advert</er>.]</ety>
<def>Not turning the mind to a matter; heedless; careless; negligent;
inattentive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An <qex>inadvertent</qex> step may crush the snail⟦br⟧
That crawls at evening in the public path.</q>
<rj><qau>Cowper.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>In`ad*vert"ent*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inadvisable</ent>⟦br⟧
